exactly the same thing.

274
00:14:53,260 --> 00:14:55,662
So you go to the first guy
and you say, "Hey",

275
00:14:55,695 --> 00:14:57,464
I want you to
repair my phone."

276
00:14:57,497 --> 00:15:00,133
And he says, "Okay, I could do
it for you at 5,000 naira."

277
00:15:00,167 --> 00:15:02,102
Now, all you have to do is
look across the road

278
00:15:02,135 --> 00:15:04,837
and find somebody who could do
exactly the same thing,

279
00:15:04,871 --> 00:15:06,306
and he knows that, right?

280
00:15:06,339 --> 00:15:08,241
So he starts to think
to himself,

281
00:15:08,275 --> 00:15:10,743
I better give him the best price
I can possibly give him...

282
00:15:10,777 --> 00:15:12,279
- Right.
- So that I can get his market.

283
00:15:12,312 --> 00:15:14,547
Completely unregulated
as far as prices.

284
00:15:14,581 --> 00:15:16,116
Completely unregulated.

285
00:15:16,149 --> 00:15:18,585
So it's really the free market
at its purest.

286
00:15:18,618 --> 00:15:20,120
Exactly.

287
00:15:20,153 --> 00:15:23,023
Lagos has been able to grow
and expand its borders

288
00:15:23,056 --> 00:15:25,392
