00:18:51,431 --> 00:18:52,932
They're very talented.

362
00:18:52,965 --> 00:18:55,235
Imagine if they were
all well-educated,

363
00:18:55,268 --> 00:18:57,337
if they had access to finance.

364
00:18:57,370 --> 00:18:59,572
I believe if
you're a black person,

365
00:18:59,606 --> 00:19:02,275
whether you're African
or you're African-American,

366
00:19:02,309 --> 00:19:04,577
you're never going to
get any respect

367
00:19:04,611 --> 00:19:08,948
unless there's a successful
black nation.

368
00:19:08,981 --> 00:19:12,219
♪

