middle finger to war...

423
00:22:02,955 --> 00:22:06,192
to corruption,
and repressive military rule.

424
00:22:06,225 --> 00:22:07,560
You know how military dictators

425
00:22:07,594 --> 00:22:09,295
try and control everything.

426
00:22:09,328 --> 00:22:11,063
But of all the music
of the time,

427
00:22:11,097 --> 00:22:13,766
nothing and nobody took it
directly to the people

428
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,836
in such explicitly
confrontational terms

429
00:22:16,869 --> 00:22:20,707
as Afrobeat and its architect,
Fela Kuti.

430
00:22:20,740 --> 00:22:23,242
The government were
giving Fela a hard time

431
00:22:23,275 --> 00:22:24,677
