by name...

432
00:22:24,711 --> 00:22:26,613
- Yeah.
- Specific things.

433
00:22:26,646 --> 00:22:29,716
I mean, they identified him
as a existential threat,

434
00:22:29,749 --> 00:22:30,850
and he was.

435
00:22:32,318 --> 00:22:33,753
